T02TD3283E:29a-1: krishna ya m'a ri sv'a dha nam /
T02TD3283E:29a-3: gshin rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3283E:29a-4: gang gi thugs rdo rje'i dbang gis nang na dgyes pa nyid yin yang //
T02TD3283E:29a-5: ma rungs gdul bya'i skye bo rnams la drag por yang dag ston //
T02TD3283E:29a-6: sna tshogs nyer phan tshun gyis gshin rje gshed yod kyang //
T02TD3283E:29a-7: gar mdzad pa yi sku de bdag gis rab tu dgod par bya //
T02TD3283E:29a-8: dang por sgrub pa po yi mchog des bde 'byung stan gnas la //
T02TD3283E:29a-9: bsam gtan gnas khang dri zhim dri yis yid ni dgar gyur par //
T02TD3283E:29a-10: bsgom par bya ste mnyam gzhag yid kyis rang gi snying gar ni /
T02TD3283E:29a-11: 'od zer gtum po'i gzugs kyi dkyil 'khor dmar po gzi ldan pa'o //
T02TD3283E:29a-12: de steng gnas pa'i h'um yig mdog sngon 'od zer dang ldan pa'i //
T02TD3283E:29a-13: 'od zer brgya byung gshin rje gshed la sogs pa rnams la ni ;
T02TD3283E:29a-14: / yid kyis sprul pa'i me tog bdug pa mar me la sogs pa //
T02TD3283E:29a-15: rnam pa mang pos legs par mchod bya gus pas phyag kyang btsal //
T02TD3283E:29a-16: sngon byas pa yi sdig pa bshags pa la sogs byas pas ni //
T02TD3283E:29a-17: stong par 'jig rten ma lus rab tu brtson par sngon bya ba //
T02TD3283E:29a-19: stong pa nyid la sogs pa'i gsang sngags tshig mchog rnams kyis bya //
T02TD3283E:29a-20: bdag nyid ngo bo gus pa nyid kyis yongs su bsgom bya ba //
T02TD3283E:29a-21: bdug pa'i 'od zer gzi brjid dang ldan dkyil 'khor dmar gnas pa'i //
T02TD3283E:29a-22: h'um yig sngon po'i gzugs las rdo rjes mtshan pa'i dbyug sngon te //
T02TD3283E:29a-23: dbyug pa la gnas h'um gzugs mchog las 'od zer dra ba rnams //
T02TD3283E:29a-24: 'phros pas legs bskul ma lus rgyal ba spyan drangs rab bcug par //
T02TD3283E:29a-25: bltas la de dag nyid ni ma lus yongs su gyur pa las ni phyis //
T02TD3283E:29a-26: bdag nyid myur bar gshin rje gshed skur yongs su bsgom bya ba //
T02TD3283E:29b-0: mthing nag sku ste khro ba @29b dad ldan zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD3283E:29b-1: phyag g-yas na ni rdo rjes mtshan pa'i dbyug to sngon po ste //
T02TD3283E:29b-2: sdigs mdzub zhags pa dang ldan g-yon pa'i phyag ni thugs kar ro //
T02TD3283E:29b-3: smad smin ser 'bar bar gyur pa'i zhal gyi padma'o //
T02TD3283E:29b-4: stag dang dzi na'i pags pa gsang ba'i phyogs su legs par bsnams //
T02TD3283E:29b-5: kha nang rnam par 'gyur ba'i ro dang ldan par gyur pa'i sprul //
T02TD3283E:29b-6: 'dab sna tshogs pa'i padma dam pa'i steng na nyi ma yi //
T02TD3283E:29b-7: gdan la legs gnas ma hirsha gtum rab tu brtson gnon pa'i //
T02TD3283E:29b-8: grod 'jol zhal sgyur mche ba rnam par gtsigs pa'i bong thung ngo //
T02TD3283E:29b-9: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gdan bzhugs sgyur bar mdzad pa'i spyan gnyis pa //
T02TD3283E:29b-10: khros pa'i klu brgyad dag gis spras pa'i rgyan ldan thod phreng gis //
T02TD3283E:29b-11: ser zhing sdug pa'i dbu skra spor ba'i 'khor lo legs par bcings //
T02TD3283E:29b-12: mi mgo las byas dam pa'i tshad ldan do shal 'chang ba can //
T02TD3283E:29b-13: ha ha cher dgod nyams kyis bdud dpung kun nas skrag par mdzad //
T02TD3283E:29b-14: phyi nas bcom ldan thugs kar gnas pa'i nyi ma la gnas par //
T02TD3283E:29b-15: h'um dbyibs 'od kyis sna tshogs kun nas gsal byas rnam par bsam //
T02TD3283E:29b-16: de la legs gzhug dus mi ring bar yang ni spro bar bya //
T02TD3283E:29b-17: rim 'dis spro dang bsdu ba ji srid 'dod kyi bar byas la //
T02TD3283E:29b-18: yang na dam tshig sngon du 'gro ba nyid kyis thams cad kyang //
T02TD3283E:29b-19: thun tshod bzhi ni 'di dag ma lus rnam par bsgom par bya //
T02TD3283E:29b-20: ngal na ji ltar brjod pa'i sngags ni rab tu bzlas par bya //
T02TD3283E:29b-21: bcom ldan gshin rje gshed kyi sgrub thabs yang mo byams pa'i dpal //
T02TD3283E:29b-22: bdag gis byas pa'i bsod nams grangs med 'dir ni gang skyes pa //
T02TD3283E:29b-23: des ni 'jig rten ma lus bcom ldan gshin rje gshed skur shog / bdag kyang ring min nyid nas gshin rje gshed du 'gyur bar shog //
T02TD3283E:29b-24: de la gsang sngags rgyal po ni 'di yin te /
T02TD3283E:29b-25: aom hr'i:shti:bi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3283E:29b-26: gshin rje gshed nag po'i sgrub thabs so /
T02TD3283E:29b-28: // / aa bha ya la sogs pa'i zhal snga nas dge slong tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bsgyur pa'o//
